text: KFI is a radio station (640 AM) in Los Angeles, California, United States. KFI may also refer to: * KPWR, a radio station (105.9 FM) in Los Angeles which used the call sign KFI-FM * KCAL-TV, a television station (channel 9 analog/43 digital) in Los Angeles which used the call sign KFI-TV * KFÍ, a basketball team in Ísafjörður, Iceland
title: KFI (disambiguation)
